<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head><%- include('partials/head') %></head>
<body>

<div class="cursor-dot" id="cursor-dot"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursor-ring"></div>
<div class="page-transition" id="page-transition"></div>

<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<main class="page-wrapper">

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner section">
      <div class="section-label reveal">01 — Hakkımda</div>
      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Kod yazarken<br><em>detaylara takılırım.</em></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT CONTENT -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="reveal">
          Merhaba! Ben <strong>Yunus Emre Tom</strong>, bir Full Stack Yazılım Geliştiricisiyim.
          Backend'den frontend'e, her katmanda kod yazmayı ve problem çözmeyi seviyorum.
          Özellikle yapay zeka, robotik sistemler ve ölçeklenebilir mimariler üzerine yoğunlaşıyorum.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Yazılıma olan ilgim ortaokul yıllarında başladı. O günden bu yana Python, C#, Java ve
          web ekosistemlerinde yoğun çalışmalar yaptım. RC uçak ve drone projeleriyle de ilgileniyorum —
          bu da bana gömülü sistemler ve gerçek zamanlı veri işleme konularında derin deneyim kazandırdı.
          Aynı zamanda lisanslı bir amatör İHA pilotuyum.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
          Yapay zeka alanında görüntü işleme (YOLO, RFDetr) ve sesli asistan projeleri üzerinde
          aktif geliştirme sürdürüyorum. ROS2 + PX4 üzerinde otonom drone kontrol sistemleri
          araştırıyorum.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
          Temiz mimari, test odaklı geliştirme ve sürdürülebilir kod benim için temel prensipler.
          Bir projeyi bitirmek değil; <em>doğru bitirmek</em> önemlidir.
        </p>
        <div class="about-actions reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <a href="/assets/cv.pdf" class="btn-primary" download>
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
            CV İndir
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline">İletişime Geç</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-stats-col">
        <div class="stats-grid-2 reveal">
          <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number"><span class="counter" data-target="7">0</span>+</div><div class="stat-label">Yıl Deneyim</div></div>
          <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number"><span class="counter" data-target="20">0</span>+</div><div class="stat-label">Proje</div></div>
          <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number"><span class="counter" data-target="5">0</span></div><div class="stat-label">Teknoloji Alanı</div></div>
          <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number">∞</div><div class="stat-label">Öğrenme</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SKILLS -->
  <section class="skills-section">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-label reveal">02 — Yetenekler</div>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Araç kutum.</h2>

      <div class="skills-blocks">
        <div class="skill-block reveal">
          <div class="skill-block-title">Backend</div>
          <div class="skill-list">
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>Python</span><span class="skill-pct">90%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="90"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>C# / C++</span><span class="skill-pct">75%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="75"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>FastAPI</span><span class="skill-pct">85%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="85"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>Java</span><span class="skill-pct">65%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="65"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-tags-row">
            <span class="skill-tag">Python</span><span class="skill-tag">FastAPI</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">C#</span><span class="skill-tag">C++</span><span class="skill-tag">Java</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-block reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="skill-block-title">Yapay Zeka & Robotik</div>
          <div class="skill-list">
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>ROS2 / PX4</span><span class="skill-pct">80%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="80"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>Computer Vision (YOLO)</span><span class="skill-pct">85%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="85"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>TTS / STT</span><span class="skill-pct">70%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="70"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-tags-row">
            <span class="skill-tag">ROS2</span><span class="skill-tag">PX4</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">YOLO</span><span class="skill-tag">OpenCV</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Gazebo</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-block reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="skill-block-title">Frontend & DevOps</div>
          <div class="skill-list">
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>HTML / CSS / JS</span><span class="skill-pct">80%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="80"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>Docker / CI-CD</span><span class="skill-pct">70%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="70"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-item-top"><span>PostgreSQL / MySQL</span><span class="skill-pct">75%</span></div>
              <div class="skill-bar-track"><div class="skill-bar-fill" data-width="75"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-tags-row">
            <span class="skill-tag">Docker</span><span class="skill-tag">Git</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Linux</span><span class="skill-tag">Nginx</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">PostgreSQL</span><span class="skill-tag">QT</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<style>
.page-hero {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding-top: 1rem;
}
.page-hero-inner { padding-bottom: 4rem; }
.page-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

.about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
.about-text p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.9; }
.about-text strong { color: var(--text); }
.about-text em { color: var(--gold); font-style: italic; }
.about-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.stats-grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }

.skills-section { background: var(--bg-card); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.skills-blocks { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
.skill-block {
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 2rem;
  transition: border-color var(--transition);
}
.skill-block:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); }
.skill-block-title {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.skill-list { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
.skill-item-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
.skill-pct { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--gold); }
.skill-tags-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  .skills-blocks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>

<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
<script src="/js/animations.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
